title: National Park Service opens bids on rehabbed oceanside home
text:
Photo: Nathaniel Y. Downes, The Chronicle Katharine Arrow of the National Park Service stands in front of the remodeled view home in Marin County. The Park Service has made the former Coast Guard housing available for rent at market prices. Katharine Arrow of the National Park Service stands in front of the...
For rent: three-bedroom, two-bath, newly remodeled Marin County house, located in parkland on an ocean cliff at the edge of the continent. Includes updated kitchen with granite countertops.
